1pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">which</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">shows the annual figures for people dying in car collisions in </span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">England</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> and Wales have fallen by 40 per cent in the past 50 years.</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt; text-indent:-28.35pt"><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="4" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 14.1pt; padding-left:14.25pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">The Department for Transport (DfT) </span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">has made significant investment in cycling in </span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">England</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> outside of </span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">London</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">for cycling in general and to tackle cycle safety specifically. However, </span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">this investment has been sporadic, rather than </span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">long term consistent funding</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">.  The level of investment, </span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">less tha</span><span style="f